<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>nginx on Notes</title><link>https://notes.harues.com/tags/nginx/</link><description>Recent content in nginx on Notes</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Mar 2021 10:00:41 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://notes.harues.com/tags/nginx/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to setup auto renew certbot certificate</title><link>https://notes.harues.com/posts/how-to-setup-auto-renew-certbot-certificate/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Mar 2021 10:00:41 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://notes.harues.com/posts/how-to-setup-auto-renew-certbot-certificate/</guid><description>&lt;p>이 글에서는 &lt;a href="https://certbot.eff.org/">&lt;code>certbot&lt;/code>&lt;/a>을 통해 발급받은 &lt;a href="https://lencr.org">Let&amp;rsquo;s Encrypt&lt;/a> 인증서를 &lt;code>Webroot&lt;/code> 플러그인을 이용한 인증서 자동 갱신 방법에 대하여 설명한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="prerequsites">Prerequsites&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Webroot 디렉터리를 생성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>이미 설정되어 있는 &lt;code>root&lt;/code> 디렉터리(&lt;code>/usr/share/nginx/html&lt;/code> 등)에 &lt;code>.well-known&lt;/code> 디렉터리를 생성해도 되지만 관리의 편의를 위하여 별도의 디렉터리를 생성한다. 디렉터리 위치는 &lt;code>/var/www/certbot&lt;/code>로 한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>sudo mkdir -p /var/www/certbot
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;h2 id="nginx-설정">Nginx 설정&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>기본 설정 파일을 열어 &lt;code>server&lt;/code>섹션에 다음 내용을 추가 한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-nginx" data-lang="nginx">&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">location&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">/.well-known/&lt;/span> {
&lt;span style="color:#f92672">root&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">/var/www/certbot/&lt;/span>;
}
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>